tps://i.imgur.com/Uu7FyfQ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I felt as Imgur’s wife of six years, it was time you heard about our marital problems. Every platform dies the same way, and you may have noticed right now that Imgur is likely deep in its own collapse. I sat down with my longtime friend TylerFromTheInternet to talk about “Ensh*ttification” - how apps hook us, bleed us, and then betray us.

https://youtu.be/jfWcoJxo7C8

Want to know what has been going on here the past couple months?

In the full video, we break down what’s happening to Imgur right now (13:27), the mass staff firings from MediaLabs (19:17), when Imgur literally broke (21:24), and how banning, blackouts, and even “The Boob Phase” (30:25) fit into the bigger picture. Along the way we hit Fark, iMDB, Reddit’s failures, and even why Mitt Romney somehow hates Tyler.

It’s funny, furious, and maybe a little depressing - but if you’ve ever loved this site, you’ll want to see how it all fits together.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/j8xtMJ7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Alsoashley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>You've Been Blessed By  Upevote Doggo</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DhPsUpA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p4pk5lZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DhPsUpA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GoogleGeneration]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Box turtles are aptly named as they can completely close up their shell like a box</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/KjmjTmH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L4rwOCy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KjmjTmH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vefivos]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Keanu got married</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9V0Qb5C</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xZUYXg3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://radaronline.com/p/keanu-reeves-artist-alexandra-grant-secretly-married/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9V0Qb5C</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ShutUpMeh]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>MOB BOSS: Stroke Me Don't Provoke Me</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ayr5UyX</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6PLMPFK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#awesome #current_affairs #australia #mildly_interesting</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ayr5UyX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OceansRust]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Here’s a good one to know</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IBM5flu</link><desc